    <div class="section-card">
      <h3>About</h3>
      <p>
        Stephen B. Heitner is Vice President and Head of Clinical Research at Cytokinetics, where he
        leads clinical development across the company‚Äôs cardiovascular portfolio, including cardiac
        myosin inhibitor programs for hypertrophic cardiomyopathy and heart failure.
        Previously, he served as Associate Professor of Medicine and Chief of the Knight
        Cardiovascular Clinical Research Institute at Oregon Health &amp; Science University (OHSU).
      </p>
      <p class="muted">
        His clinical practice has focused on patients with hypertrophic cardiomyopathy, cardiac
        amyloidosis and other complex cardiomyopathies, integrating advanced echocardiography and
        multi-modality imaging to guide diagnosis and management.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="focus">
    <div class="section-card grid-2">
