        <h3>Clinical &amp; Research Focus</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Hypertrophic cardiomyopathy (obstructive and non-obstructive)</li>
          <li>Cardiac amyloidosis and infiltrative cardiomyopathies</li>
          <li>Cardio-oncology and complex cardiomyopathy care</li>
          <li>Targeted therapies for sarcomeric disease, including cardiac myosin inhibitors</li>
          <li>Advanced echocardiography and structural heart imaging</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="muted">
          Across both academia and industry, Dr. Heitner has been involved in designing and leading
          multicenter clinical trials, with a particular emphasis on translating mechanistic insights
          in sarcomere biology into disease-modifying therapies for patients with cardiomyopathy.
        </p>
